  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male/female at least 18 years of age

          -  Agree to avoid disallowed medications

          -  Have a diagnosis of dry eye

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Have chronic systemic inflammation

          -  Have active seasonal ocular allergies
      </textblock>
